lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Vera Zvonareva beat Lucie Hradecka, 6-2, 6-3, in the first round of the Prague Open. Jill Craybas of the United States also advanced to the second round with a 6-4, 6-2 victory against fifth-seeded Karin Knapp.
